COUNT OUT> +! DROP  ELSE   >R DUP COUNT R@ +  CR   ." tail is " 0 SWAP -  HEX. ." bytes "  THEN ;    
: HEXt   HERE @ SWAP 0x, 8 HERE @ C! HERE @ 1+ HEXa S>>#   ;   
